text: The 1st hearing for the U.S. Workforce Act, which I intro'd in the House and @lisamurkowski in the Senate, is set for tomorrow (Wed. 1am in the NMI, Tue. 10am in DC). I will be outlining the bill to the Senate Energy and Natural Resources Committee, which @lisamurkowski chairs.

To those who've already followed this account: 

We now are at the handle @Kilili_Sablan and no longer @SablanKilili. We are now working on Twitter verification. Thank you for your patience as we set up this account.
